ComicInfo.Summary: F5, a story revolving around 12 young members of an elite and secret task force, who hide out as Weathermen" or stormtracking Meteorologists, fills the action/adventure void that today's fans are craving! The fans wanted it, they got it! F5 will undoubtedly and immodestly be one of the decade's most action packed and character driven books produced! That "Whooshing" sound was the readers rushing out the door with their copy of F5#1! F5's first mission finds them over the waters of the Atlantic Ocean, as they uncover a true mystery at sea. Scientists and US Soldiers onboard the USS Hurricane have disappeared and all that's left is a damaged ship. Spies have sabotaged a top secret research expedition and walked away with newly found and very lethal chemical that can be used in Germ Warfare! This leads Penny, the leader of F5, and her team on an intense search-and-destroy mission through Europe that ends in Russia to uncover the sinister and diabolical mastermind. Explosive shootouts, dangerous liaisons and cinematic qualities bring this story to life! Created, written and penciled by Tony Daniel (X-Force, Spawn, The Tenth, Adrenalynn), this giant sized debut issue is sure to please all! 48 pages of heart pounding excitement and adventure, in full color. Features a special pull out poster!
